<plot>Three years after taping his previous show in the Persian Gulf, Bob Hope returns to the front line to put on another USO Christmas extravaganza, this time in Saudi Arabia for US Troops preparing with other nations to expel Iraq's 1990 invasion and attempted annexation of Kuwait. Contains a hilarious dialogue sketch between Hope and former "Head of the Class" starlet Khrystyne Haje.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?077096</url></doc>
